<blockquote>
<p>随便写点啥都行。<span style="text-decoration: line-through;">说得好像会有人留言一样。</span> ——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/raintree" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5375092); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5375092&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663906" alt="RainTree" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5375092)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/raintree" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5375092); return false;">RainTree</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p><span style="text-decoration: line-through;">说得好像有人不会留言一样！呜呜呜……</span>这个丛雨头像我好了！ ——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/timeelapsed" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3662783); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3662783&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663906" alt="TimeElapsed" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3662783)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/timeelapsed" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3662783); return false;">TimeElapsed</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>绝了 ——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/onxy" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3258233); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3258233&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663906" alt="ONXY" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3258233)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/onxy" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3258233); return false;">ONXY</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>绝了 ——喜欢复读的<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ctorjschen" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4530800); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4530800&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663906" alt="CTorJSChen" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4530800)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ctorjschen" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4530800); return false;">CTorJSChen</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>[脸滚键盘] ——<span style="text-decoration: line-through;">被误称为前辈的</span><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jonuarl-reden" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3740635); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3740635&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663906" alt="Jonuarl Reden" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3740635)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jonuarl-reden" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3740635); return false;">Jonuarl Reden</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p><span style="text-decoration: line-through;">www，留言点编辑就可以的吗</span>，第一次在基金会给别人留言诶，那么，<span style="text-decoration: line-through;">绝了</span>——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-obsidian-shard" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5090298); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5090298&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663906" alt="The Obsidian Shard" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5090298)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-obsidian-shard" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5090298); return false;">The Obsidian Shard</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>绝了，不愧是你。——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-naxurt" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4423816); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4423816&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663906" alt="Dr_Naxurt" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4423816)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-naxurt" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4423816); return false;">Dr_Naxurt</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
