<div id="wiki-tab-0-0">
<div class="image-container floatleft"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/hal-aki-achievement-badges/%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E5%8F%82%E5%8A%A0%E8%A1%A8%E6%98%8E.png" width="50" alt="%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E5%8F%82%E5%8A%A0%E8%A1%A8%E6%98%8E.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:120%;"><span style="color:#970118"><strong>加入证明</strong></span></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>被批准加入网站</strong></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>这个ID叫RainTree的家伙出现了</strong></span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<div class="image-container floatleft"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/hal-aki-achievement-badges/%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E3%81%AF%E3%81%98%E3%82%81%E3%81%BE%E3%81%97%E3%81%A6%E3%81%AE%E6%8C%A8%E6%8B%B6.png" width="50" alt="%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E3%81%AF%E3%81%98%E3%82%81%E3%81%BE%E3%81%97%E3%81%A6%E3%81%AE%E6%8C%A8%E6%8B%B6.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:120%;"><span style="color:#970118"><strong>初次见面</strong></span></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>在讨论区发言</strong></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>有人还记得我第一次说了啥吗？</strong></span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<div class="image-container floatleft"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/hal-aki-achievement-badges/%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E7%A7%98%E5%AF%86%E3%81%AE%E5%AE%9F%E9%A8%93%E5%AE%A4.png" width="50" alt="%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E7%A7%98%E5%AF%86%E3%81%AE%E5%AE%9F%E9%A8%93%E5%AE%A4.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:120%;"><span style="color:#970118"><strong>秘密实验室</strong></span></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>在沙盒中创建自己的页面</strong></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>开始写第一篇神风文</strong></span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<div class="image-container floatleft"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/hal-aki-achievement-badges/%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E4%B8%89%E4%BA%BA%E5%AF%84%E3%82%8C%E3%81%B0.png" width="50" alt="%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E4%B8%89%E4%BA%BA%E5%AF%84%E3%82%8C%E3%81%B0.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:120%;"><span style="color:#970118"><strong>三人行</strong></span></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>在讨论区发布草稿</strong></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>神风文没人看，导致后来死的很惨</strong></span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<div class="image-container floatleft"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/hal-aki-achievement-badges/%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E5%B0%8F%E3%81%95%E3%81%AA%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A9.png" width="50" alt="%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E5%B0%8F%E3%81%95%E3%81%AA%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A9.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:120%;"><span style="color:#970118"><strong>一小步</strong></span></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>发布一篇文档</strong></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>因为是神风，死得很快</strong></span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<div class="image-container floatleft"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/hal-aki-achievement-badges/%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E6%8E%A1%E7%94%A8%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5.png" width="50" alt="%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E6%8E%A1%E7%94%A8%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:120%;"><span style="color:#970118"><strong>录取通知</strong></span></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>创建人事档案</strong></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>开始想自己的设定</strong></span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<div class="image-container floatleft"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/hal-aki-achievement-badges/%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E9%8A%85%E3%83%A1%E3%83%80%E3%83%AB.png" width="50" alt="%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E9%8A%85%E3%83%A1%E3%83%80%E3%83%AB.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:120%;"><span style="color:#970118"><strong>铜奖章</strong></span></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>发布一篇评分15以上的文档</strong></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>SCP-CN-1848，第一篇活下来的文档</strong></span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<div class="image-container floatleft"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/hal-aki-achievement-badges/%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E9%8A%80%E3%83%A1%E3%83%80%E3%83%AB.png" width="50" alt="%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E9%8A%80%E3%83%A1%E3%83%80%E3%83%AB.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:120%;"><span style="color:#970118"><strong>银奖章</strong></span></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>发布一篇评分30以上的文档</strong></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>还是SCP-CN-1848，说实话，挺出乎我意料的</strong></span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<div class="image-container floatleft"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/hal-aki-achievement-badges/%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E3%81%BF%E3%81%AA%E3%82%89%E3%81%84%E3%83%BB%E3%81%8B%E3%81%9F%E3%82%8A%E3%81%B9.png" width="50" alt="%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E3%81%BF%E3%81%AA%E3%82%89%E3%81%84%E3%83%BB%E3%81%8B%E3%81%9F%E3%82%8A%E3%81%B9.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:120%;"><span style="color:#970118"><strong>说书人学徒</strong></span></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>发布5篇以上的故事</strong></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>因为写故事比写文档来的简单嘛……（托腮）</strong></span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<div class="image-container floatleft"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/hal-aki-achievement-badges/%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E3%81%8A%E7%A5%AD%E3%82%8A%E5%A5%BD%E3%81%8D.png" width="50" alt="%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E3%81%8A%E7%A5%AD%E3%82%8A%E5%A5%BD%E3%81%8D.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:120%;"><span style="color:#970118"><strong>喜欢祭典</strong></span></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>参加一次竞赛</strong></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>《凄凄白夜》，我在基金会的第一篇故事</strong></span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<div class="image-container floatleft"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/hal-aki-achievement-badges/%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E3%83%80%E3%82%A4%E3%82%B9%E3%82%AD%E3%83%9F%E3%83%A4%E3%82%B6%E3%83%AF.png" width="50" alt="%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E3%83%80%E3%82%A4%E3%82%B9%E3%82%AD%E3%83%9F%E3%83%A4%E3%82%B6%E3%83%AF.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:120%;"><span style="color:#970118"><strong>DAFU GONGCHUAN</strong></span></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>在竞赛中获胜</strong></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>第二名和季军……应该算吧（大概）</strong></span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<div class="image-container floatleft"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/hal-aki-achievement-badges/%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E5%AD%A6%E8%80%85.png" width="50" alt="%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E5%AD%A6%E8%80%85.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:120%;"><span style="color:#970118"><strong>生物学家</strong></span></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>发布一篇评分20以上的、包含下列任一标签的SCP文档：生物性、活物、基因、动物、植物、细菌</strong></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>SCP-CN-1848，因为好写（即答）</strong></span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<div class="image-container floatleft"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/hal-aki-achievement-badges/%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6%E8%80%85.png" width="50" alt="%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6%E8%80%85.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:120%;"><span style="color:#970118"><strong>心理学家</strong></span></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>发布一篇评分20以上的、包含下列任一标签的SCP文档：精神影响、模因、强迫性、移情作用、记忆影响、知识</strong></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>SCP-CN-1747，因为好写（复读）</strong></span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<div class="image-container floatleft"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/hal-aki-achievement-badges/%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E6%97%85%E4%BA%BA.png" width="50" alt="%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E6%97%85%E4%BA%BA.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:120%;"><span style="color:#970118"><strong>旅行家</strong></span></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>发布一篇评分20以上的、包含下列任一标签的SCP文档：时空、未来、超维度、地图、门径</strong></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>SCP-CN-1747</strong></span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<div class="image-container floatleft"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/hal-aki-achievement-badges/%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E5%BB%BA%E7%AF%89%E5%AE%B6.png" width="50" alt="%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E5%BB%BA%E7%AF%89%E5%AE%B6.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:120%;"><span style="color:#970118"><strong>建筑学家</strong></span></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>发布一篇评分20以上的、包含下列任一标签的SCP文档：城市、建筑家、地点</strong></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>SCP-CN-1545</strong></span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<div class="image-container floatleft"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/hal-aki-achievement-badges/%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E3%83%8B%E3%83%A5%E3%83%BC%E3%83%88%E3%83%A9%E3%83%A9%E3%83%A9%E3%82%A4%E3%82%B9%E3%83%89.png" width="50" alt="%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E3%83%8B%E3%83%A5%E3%83%BC%E3%83%88%E3%83%A9%E3%83%A9%E3%83%A9%E3%82%A4%E3%82%B9%E3%83%89.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:120%;"><span style="color:#970118"><strong>无效攵攵攵化</strong></span></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>发布一篇评分20以上、关于Neutralized级项目的SCP文档</strong></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>SCP-CN-1848</strong></span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<div class="image-container floatleft"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/hal-aki-achievement-badges/%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E8%AA%B0%E3%81%8B%E3%81%AE%E6%97%A5%E5%B8%B8.png" width="50" alt="%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E8%AA%B0%E3%81%8B%E3%81%AE%E6%97%A5%E5%B8%B8.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:120%;"><span style="color:#970118"><strong>某人的日常</strong></span></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>发布一篇评分20以上的、不包含基金会工作人员的故事</strong></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>《冷雨》，我个人很喜欢的一篇</strong></span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<div class="image-container floatleft"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/hal-aki-achievement-badges/%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_SCP%E3%81%AF%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E3%82%92%E3%81%A4%E3%81%AA%E3%81%90.png" width="50" alt="%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_SCP%E3%81%AF%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E3%82%92%E3%81%A4%E3%81%AA%E3%81%90.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:120%;"><span style="color:#970118"><strong>SCP连接世界</strong></span></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>根据以日本支部以外的支部或本站的文档，发布一篇评分20以上的故事</strong></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>《凄凄白夜》，根据SCP-8900-EX所写</strong></span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<div class="image-container floatleft"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/hal-aki-achievement-badges/%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E3%81%BF%E3%82%93%E3%81%AA%E3%81%A7%E3%81%A4%E3%81%8F%E3%82%8D%E3%81%86.png" width="50" alt="%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E3%81%BF%E3%82%93%E3%81%AA%E3%81%A7%E3%81%A4%E3%81%8F%E3%82%8D%E3%81%86.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:120%;"><span style="color:#970118"><strong>大家一起来</strong></span></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>发布一篇合作文档</strong></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>SCP-CN-1734，感谢<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yixi-windbell" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5867553); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5867553&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663906" alt="yixi_Windbell" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5867553)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yixi-windbell" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5867553); return false;">yixi_Windbell</a></span>酱与我合著</strong></span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<div class="image-container floatleft"><img src="http://scpsandboxcn.wdfiles.com/local--files/fragment%3Aylumwlne-1/10.png" width="50" alt="10.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:120%;"><span style="color:#970118"><strong>整好活</strong></span></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>2020画廊大赛@<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yuannn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6062512); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6062512&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663906" alt="YUANNN" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6062512)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yuannn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6062512); return false;">YUANNN</a></span>挑战奖：在比赛中创作一篇带有crossover标签的作品，并在同类稿件中取得唯一最高分。</strong></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>《赌》，个人觉得 <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">没有《冷雨》好</span> 写的一坨狗屎</strong></span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<div class="image-container floatleft"><img src="http://scpsandboxcn.wdfiles.com/local--files/fragment%3Aylumwlne-1/11.png" width="50" alt="11.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:120%;"><span style="color:#970118"><strong>来了，走了，我的一生结束了</strong></span></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>2020画廊大赛@<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-obsidian-shard" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5090298); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5090298&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663906" alt="The Obsidian Shard" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5090298)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-obsidian-shard" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5090298); return false;">The Obsidian Shard</a></span>挑战奖：在比赛中创作一篇以反乌托邦为背景的故事，描绘主人公的一生。要求使用“死者手牌”或“最冷之战”两个设定中的一个。取全排名前3/5中的唯一最高分。</strong></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>《冷雨》，个人最喜欢的一篇，感谢<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ylumwlne" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5450442); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5450442&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663906" alt="Ylumwlne" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5450442)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ylumwlne" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5450442); return false;">Ylumwlne</a></span>绘制的logo！</strong></span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
